11. Music-Genre:countrys is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:liverpoolmaster == Movie-Genre:western
13. Flower:balloon-flower == Cigar:prince
14. Flower:sunflower is on the left or right of City:liverpool
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:martial-arts

